OL,3,CChild dies after suspected dog attack
OL,4,Cin North Yorkshire
OL,6,FA child has died as a result of a dog
OL,7,Fbite at a property in North Yorkshire.
OL,9,FOfficers were called to an address on
OL,10,FHardale Grove in Dormanstown, Redcar,
OL,11,Fshortly after 1:30pm on Thursday,
OL,12,FCleveland Police said.
OL,14,FPolice said that the child had already
OL,15,Fdied upon their arrival at the
OL,16,Fproperty.
OL,18,FArmed officers attended and one dog
OL,19,Fwas destroyed on the street. Another
OL,20,Fdog at the property has been recovered
OL,21,Fby police, the force said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
