OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775823074
OL,3,CChild dies after suspected dog attack
OL,4,Cin North Yorkshire
OL,6,FITV News does not currently know the
OL,7,Fbreed of the dog.
OL,9,FDistrict Commander for Redcar and
OL,10,FCleveland, Emily Harrison said:
OL,11,F"Understandably this is a distressing
OL,12,Fand tragic incident, and our thoughts
OL,13,Fare with the child's family.
OL,15,F"There is a scene in place at the
OL,16,Faddress while an investigation into
OL,17,Fthe child's death begins.
OL,19,F"I would encourage anyone who has
OL,20,Fconcerns or information to please
OL,21,Fspeak to an officer."
