OL,3,CChild dies after suspected dog attack
OL,4,Cin North Yorkshire
OL,6,FA North East Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We were called to
OL,8,Fan incident at a private address in
OL,9,FRedcar on Thursday April 9 shortly
OL,10,Fbefore 1.30pm.
OL,12,F"We dispatched three ambulance crews,
OL,13,Fone clinical team leader and one duty
OL,14,Fofficer to the incident.
OL,16,F"One patient was transported to
OL,17,Fhospital for further treatment."
